## Overview

This task involves a comprehensive audit of database tables to identify unused fields that can be safely removed. The investigation will help reduce database complexity, improve maintainability, and ensure our codebase and database schema remain aligned. The main idea is to investigate and review database tables containing fields that are not being used in the codebase, with the goal of performing a cleanup in both the database and the code.

